# Local data snapshots pulled from Firestore (contain staff IC numbers / PII).
# Regenerate anytime with `npm run pull`; never commit to the public repo.
# NOTE: must live OUTSIDE public/ — anything under public/ is bundled into dist/
# by Vite and deployed publicly. Snapshots now go to ./data (see pull_from_prod.js).
